selector_to_html = {"a[href=\"system.html#volume-settings\"]": "<h2 class=\"tippy-header\" style=\"margin-top: 0;\">Configura\u00e7\u00f5es de Volume<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#volume-settings\" title=\"Link to this heading\">#</a></h2><p>Digitalize o c\u00f3digo de configura\u00e7\u00e3o correspondente para ativar/desativar o prompt de som do scanner</p>", "a[href=\"system.html\"]": "<h1 class=\"tippy-header\" style=\"margin-top: 0;\">Configura\u00e7\u00f5es do Sistema<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#system-settings\" title=\"Link to this heading\">#</a></h1><h2>Restaurar configura\u00e7\u00f5es padr\u00e3o<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#restore-default-settings\" title=\"Link to this heading\">#</a></h2><p>Quando um erro desconhecido ocorre no scanner, voc\u00ea pode redefinir o scanner restaurando as configura\u00e7\u00f5es padr\u00e3o.</p>", "a[href=\"working.html\"]": "<h1 class=\"tippy-header\" style=\"margin-top: 0;\">Modo de trabalho<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#working-mode\" title=\"Link to this heading\">#</a></h1><p>Na \u00e1rea de trabalho fora do limite de 2. Receptor G ou sinal Bluetooth, voc\u00ea pode ativar o modo de armazenamento do scanner, seguindo as etapas descritas abaixo. Neste modo, todos os dados digitalizados ser\u00e3o armazenados diretamente no scanner. Antes de enviar os dados, ser\u00e1 guardado permanentemente no scanner para que voc\u00ea possa carregar os dados quando o scanner estiver no intervalo de sinal de recebimento.</p>", "a[href=\"working.html#storage-mode\"]": "<h2 class=\"tippy-header\" style=\"margin-top: 0;\">Modo de armazenamento<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#storage-mode\" title=\"Link to this heading\">#</a></h2><h3>Envio de dados<a class=\"footnote-reference brackets\" href=\"#id2\" id=\"id1\" role=\"doc-noteref\"><span class=\"fn-bracket\">[</span>1<span class=\"fn-bracket\">]</span></a><a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#data-upload1\" title=\"Link to this heading\">#</a></h3>", "a[href=\"bluetooth.html\"]": "<h1 class=\"tippy-header\" style=\"margin-top: 0;\">Modo Bluetooth<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#bluetooth-mode\" title=\"Link to this heading\">#</a></h1>", "a[href=\"process.html#output-format\"]": "<h2 class=\"tippy-header\" style=\"margin-top: 0;\">Formato de sa\u00edda<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#output-format\" title=\"Link to this heading\">#</a></h2><p>Para alterar o formato de transmiss\u00e3o de dados, digitalize um dos oito c\u00f3digos de barras correspondentes ao formato desejado.</p>", "a[href=\"process.html#hide-set\"]": "<h2 class=\"tippy-header\" style=\"margin-top: 0;\">Esconder Conjunto<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#hide-set\" title=\"Link to this heading\">#</a></h2><h3>Esconder c\u00f3digos de barras iniciando<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#hide-barcode-start-chars\" title=\"Link to this heading\">#</a></h3>", "a[href=\"process.html#prefix\"]": "<h2 class=\"tippy-header\" style=\"margin-top: 0;\">Prefixo<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#prefix\" title=\"Link to this heading\">#</a></h2><h3>Adicionar Prefixo<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#add-prefix\" title=\"Link to this heading\">#</a></h3>", "a[href=\"process.html#quick-setup\"]": "<h2 class=\"tippy-header\" style=\"margin-top: 0;\">Configura\u00e7\u00e3o R\u00e1pida<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#quick-setup\" title=\"Link to this heading\">#</a></h2><h3>Adicionar Prefixo<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#id3\" title=\"Link to this heading\">#</a></h3>", "a[href=\"process.html#suffix\"]": "<h2 class=\"tippy-header\" style=\"margin-top: 0;\">Suffix<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#suffix\" title=\"Link to this heading\">#</a></h2><h3>Adicionar Sufixo<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#add-suffix\" title=\"Link to this heading\">#</a></h3>", "a[href=\"keyboard.html#case-settings\"]": "<h2 class=\"tippy-header\" style=\"margin-top: 0;\">Configura\u00e7\u00f5es Caso<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#case-settings\" title=\"Link to this heading\">#</a></h2><h3>normal<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#normal\" title=\"Link to this heading\">#</a></h3>", "a[href=\"process.html\"]": "<h1 class=\"tippy-header\" style=\"margin-top: 0;\">Edi\u00e7\u00e3o de dados<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#data-editing\" title=\"Link to this heading\">#</a></h1><h2>Formato de sa\u00edda<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#output-format\" title=\"Link to this heading\">#</a></h2><p>Para alterar o formato de transmiss\u00e3o de dados, digitalize um dos oito c\u00f3digos de barras correspondentes ao formato desejado.</p>", "a[href=\"process.html#appendix\"]": "<h2 class=\"tippy-header\" style=\"margin-top: 0;\">Ap\u00eandice<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#appendix\" title=\"Link to this heading\">#</a></h2><h3>C\u00f3digos de barras num\u00e9ricas<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#numeric-bar-codes\" title=\"Link to this heading\">#</a></h3>", "a[href=\"working.html#normal-mode\"]": "<h2 class=\"tippy-header\" style=\"margin-top: 0;\">Modo normal<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#normal-mode\" title=\"Link to this heading\">#</a></h2>", "a[href=\"system.html#get-firmware-version\"]": "<h2 class=\"tippy-header\" style=\"margin-top: 0;\">Obter vers\u00e3o do Firmware<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#get-firmware-version\" title=\"Link to this heading\">#</a></h2>", "a[href=\"system.html#battery-information\"]": "<h2 class=\"tippy-header\" style=\"margin-top: 0;\">Informa\u00e7\u00f5es da bateria<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#battery-information\" title=\"Link to this heading\">#</a></h2>", "a[href=\"keyboard.html#keyboard-language\"]": "<h2 class=\"tippy-header\" style=\"margin-top: 0;\">Idioma do teclado<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#keyboard-language\" title=\"Link to this heading\">#</a></h2><h3>Obter o idioma atual do teclado<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#get-current-keyboard-language\" title=\"Link to this heading\">#</a></h3>", "a[href=\"keyboard.html\"]": "<h1 class=\"tippy-header\" style=\"margin-top: 0;\">Configura\u00e7\u00f5es de teclado<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#keyboard-settings\" title=\"Link to this heading\">#</a></h1><h2>Configura\u00e7\u00f5es Caso<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#case-settings\" title=\"Link to this heading\">#</a></h2><h3>normal<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#normal\" title=\"Link to this heading\">#</a></h3>", "a[href=\"#rs-9000bt-wireless-scanner-quick-setup-guide\"]": "<h1 class=\"tippy-header\" style=\"margin-top: 0;\">Guia de configura\u00e7\u00e3o r\u00e1pida do scanner sem fios <strong>RS-9000BT</strong><a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#rs-9000bt-wireless-scanner-quick-setup-guide\" title=\"Link to this heading\">#</a></h1>", "a[href=\"system.html#sleep-time\"]": "<h2 class=\"tippy-header\" style=\"margin-top: 0;\">Hora de dormir<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#sleep-time\" title=\"Link to this heading\">#</a></h2><p>Ao escanear o seguinte c\u00f3digo de configura\u00e7\u00e3o, voc\u00ea pode definir o scanner para entrar em modo de suspens\u00e3o ap\u00f3s um determinado per\u00edodo de tempo quando nenhum c\u00f3digo \u00e9 escaneado, para reduzir o consumo de energia.</p>", "a[href=\"system.html#restore-default-settings\"]": "<h2 class=\"tippy-header\" style=\"margin-top: 0;\">Restaurar configura\u00e7\u00f5es padr\u00e3o<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#restore-default-settings\" title=\"Link to this heading\">#</a></h2><p>Quando um erro desconhecido ocorre no scanner, voc\u00ea pode redefinir o scanner restaurando as configura\u00e7\u00f5es padr\u00e3o.</p>"}
skip_classes = ["headerlink", "sd-stretched-link", "sd-rounded-pill"]

window.onload = function () {
    for (const [select, tip_html] of Object.entries(selector_to_html)) {
        const links = document.querySelectorAll(`article.bd-article ${select}`);
        for (const link of links) {
            if (skip_classes.some(c => link.classList.contains(c))) {
                continue;
            }

            tippy(link, {
                content: tip_html,
                allowHTML: true,
                arrow: true,
                placement: 'auto-start', maxWidth: 500, interactive: false,

            });
        };
    };
    console.log("tippy tips loaded!");
};
